---
type Props = {
  title: string;
  path: string;
};

const { title, path } = Astro.props;
---

<section class="shell section-divider">
  <div class="stack">
    <article class="detail-card">
      <p class="eyebrow">Legal</p>
      <h1>{title}</h1>
      <p>
        This page combines the Burning Tree MMA Privacy Policy and Terms of Service in
        one place for easy reference. The same combined content is available at both
        `/privacy` and `/terms`.
      </p>
      <p>
        Current route:
        <strong> {path}</strong>
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="detail-card">
      <p class="eyebrow">Privacy Policy</p>
      <h2>How we collect and use information</h2>
      <div class="benefit-list">
        <p>
          Burning Tree MMA may collect information you submit through website forms,
          including your name, phone number, program interest, and any optional comments.
        </p>
        <p>
          We use this information to respond to inquiries, help you choose the right
          program, follow up about class availability, and improve the customer experience.
        </p>
        <p>
          We may store or process submitted information through trusted tools used for
          website hosting, forms, analytics, or lead routing, including future Make.com
          webhook integrations.
        </p>
        <p>
          We do not sell your personal information. We only share it when needed to
          operate the site, manage communications, comply with legal obligations, or
          protect the business and our users.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you would like your submitted information updated or removed, contact
          Burning Tree MMA directly using the contact details listed on this site.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="detail-card">
      <p class="eyebrow">Terms of Service</p>
      <h2>Using the website</h2>
      <div class="benefit-list">
        <p>
          By using this website, you agree to use it only for lawful purposes and in a
          way that does not interfere with the site, the business, or other users.
        </p>
        <p>
          Website content, branding, logos, copy, and design elements belong to Burning
          Tree MMA unless otherwise stated and may not be copied or reused without
          permission.
        </p>
        <p>
          Information on this site is provided for general informational and marketing
          purposes. Program details, schedules, offers, and availability may change
          without notice.
        </p>
        <p>
          Submitting a form or contacting the business through the website does not
          guarantee enrollment, availability, or any specific offer unless confirmed by
          Burning Tree MMA directly.
        </p>
        <p>
          Burning Tree MMA may update these terms and the privacy policy from time to
          time. Continued use of the website after updates means you accept the revised
          terms.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
